## 3. WebResponse — HTTP Response Builder

`WebResponse` wraps entities/lists for JSON API responses.

```rust
// From single entity
let response = WebResponse::from_entity(&task);

// From list with pagination
let response = WebResponse::from_smart_list(task_list);

// Error response
let response = WebResponse::fail("Invalid request");
```

| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `WebResponse::from_entity(&e)` | Wrap single entity |
| `WebResponse::from_smart_list(list)` | Wrap paginated list |
| `WebResponse::fail(msg)` | Create error response |
| `.to_json_value()` | Serialize to `serde_json::Value` |

