## 4. AuditConfig — Logging Control

Controls what the runtime logs. Configured via environment variables.

### Environment Variables
| Variable | Values | Default |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `TEAQL_AUDIT` | `verbose`, `production`, `silent` | `production` |
| `TEAQL_SCHEMA` | `execute`, `dry_run`, `verify` | `execute` |
| `TEAQL_SQL_LOG` | `all`, `select`, `mutation`, `off` | `off` |

### Programmatic Config
```rust
let config = AuditConfig::production();       // normal logging
let config = AuditConfig::verbose_all();      // maximum detail
let config = AuditConfig::silent_all();       // no logging
let config = AuditConfig::focus_on(Module::Mutation); // focus on writes
```

