## 5. Schema Management

Database schema is auto-managed. No manual SQL needed.

```rust
// In startup
ctx.ensure_schema().await?;
// This will:
// - Create tables that don't exist
// - Add columns for new properties
// - Never drop columns or tables (safe)
```

| SchemaMode | Behavior |
|------------|----------|
| `Execute` | Apply schema changes automatically |
| `DryRun` | Log what would change, don't apply |
| `Verify` | Fail if schema doesn't match |

