## 6. EntityGraph — Batch Save

Save an entity and all its related children/parents in one operation.

```rust
// Single entity save
task.audit_as("Update task name").save(&ctx).await?;

// This automatically:
// 1. Checks auditAs is set (Triple-Intent)
// 2. Runs checkers
// 3. Diffs against DB state
// 4. Generates INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE SQL
// 5. Writes audit log
// 6. Fires entity events
```

